This project uses the quasi-steady-state lap time simulation algorithm
inspired by research from TUM Fast Technology Munich (TUMFTM), whose
original implementations are licensed under LGPL-3.0.

By using LGPL-3.0 for this project, we maintain compatibility with
TUMFTM's licensing while respecting their excellent research and
open-source contributions.

For the full text of the GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0, visit:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0.en.html

