ACADEMIC ATTRIBUTION:

This implementation is based on research from:

Christ, F., Wischnewski, A., Heilmeier, A., & Lohmann, B. (2019).
"Time-Optimal Trajectory Planning for a Race Car Considering Variable 
Tyre-Road Friction Coefficients." Vehicle System Dynamics, 59(4), 588-612.
DOI: 10.1080/00423114.2019.1704804

Heilmeier, A., Graf, M., & Lienkamp, M. (2018).
"A Race Simulation for Strategy Decisions in Circuit Motorsports."
2018 21st International Conference on Intelligent Transportation Systems (ITSC).
DOI: 10.1109/itsc.2018.8570012

TUMFTM Repositories:
- https://github.com/TUMFTM/laptime-simulation
- https://github.com/TUMFTM/global_racetrajectory_optimization
- https://github.com/TUMFTM/racetrack-database
